<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̹dyny ạ̉mạnẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ạ̹dyny ạ̉mạnẗ lyk wqt ạlạ̹ymạn mạ yumtḥn
 wạḥmyny bmḥbẗ lyk ạ̉ḥyạ bqdạsẗ wqt ạlmḥn)2
 ạlqrạr- (wạlnʿmẗ ạlly mạlkẗ qlby bạlbr wbạlḍyạʾ
 tʿln ạ̹n ạ̹nt rby fy ḥyạty kmạ fy ạlsmạʾ)2
 2- (ạ̹dyny ạ̉mạnẗ lyk fy ạlṣgẖyr wạlqlyl wạzyd mtdạry fyk wạltẖmạr tbqy̱ ạldlyl)2
 3- (ạ̹dyny ạ̉mạnẗ lyk fy ạlwkạlẗ ʿly̱ ạlḥyạẗ wạʿysẖ lywm mjyỷk mtḥạwṭ btrs ạlrḍạ)2</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1368</hymn_number>
<author>mạhr fạyz, mạhr fạyz</author>
</song>